CBRE Hotels is pleased to present to market tavern @ the rocks â€“ a large Freehold Going Concern tavern located in Perth's expanding northern corridor. 

Positioned within the Two Rocks Marina precinct, this 2,864sqm* site offers an incoming purchaser the opportunity to grow the business as well as future development upside as Two Rocks and the greater North West coastal corridor expands.

Investment Highlights: 

- An established tavern comprising bistro dining, TAB sports bar, lounge bar, large function areas, outdoor alfresco, Manager's residence and a disused drive-thru bottleshop
- Licensed for 912* patrons
- Ample on-site car parking 
- No direct competing venues within the precinct 
- Significant landholding of 2,864sqm* with future development upside

Tavern @ the rocks is for sale by Private Treaty. Contact selling agents for a price guide, to obtain a copy of the information memorandum or to arrange an inspection.

*approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Cuddles Childcare Atlantis offers a brand new, purpose built childcare facility in Perth's northern corridor. A 15 year lease to Cuddles Childcare will commence in September 2018 and the centre will offer places for 100 children.

Significant depreciation benefits and fixed 3% annual increases make this a financially attractive investment. 

Cuddles Childcare Centre is For Sale via Public Auction on 22nd June 2018 at 11:00am. For further information, please contact the exclusive sales and marketing agents.
